Class NotificationLog

java.lang.Object
com.example.zephyr_lottery.models.NotificationLog
public class NotificationLog extends Object
Model for notification audit log entries for admins. Stored in the "notificationLogs" collection.

      eventId - The ID of the event that the notification applies to
      eventName - The name of the event that the notification applies to
      senderEmail - The email of the creator of the event
      userId - The ID of the notification recipient
      notificationType - The type of the notification
      sentAt - The time the notification was sent at, as a Timestamp
